<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>WastedToken Mint</title>
<style>
  body{margin:0;font-family:sans-serif;background:#f4f4f4;color:#333;}
  header{background:#222;color:white;padding:2rem;text-align:center;}
  h1{margin:0;font-size:2.5rem;}
  section{padding:2rem;max-width:1200px;margin:auto;}
  .about{font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.6;}
  .grid{display:grid;gap:1rem;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));}
  .edition{background:white;border-radius:.5rem;padding:1rem;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1);}
  .edition-canvas{width:100%;height:200px;background:#eee;}
  button.buy{margin-top:.5rem;padding:.5rem 1rem;font-size:1rem;border:none;border-radius:.3rem;background:#28a745;color:white;cursor:pointer;}
  button.buy[disabled]{background:#aaa;cursor:not-allowed;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header id="hero-header">
  <h1>WastedToken Mint</h1>
</header>

<section id="hero-section" style="text-align:center;">
  <canvas id="coin-hero" width="400" height="400"></canvas>
</section>

<section class="about">
  <p>At WastedToken Mint we craft limited‑edition challenge coins that celebrate
  the spirit of play and the thrill of collection. Each coin is hand‑finished,
  with a raised emblem, a crisp denomination on the reverse, and a
  meticulously reeded edge that gleams under any light.</p>
</section>

<section class="collection">
  <h2>Our Editions</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="edition" data-edition="bronze" data-state="available">
      <canvas class="edition-canvas"></canvas>
      <button class="buy">Add to cart</button>
    </div>
    <div class="edition" data-edition="silver" data-state="available">
      <canvas class="edition-canvas"></canvas>
      <button class="buy">Add to cart</button>
    </div>
